description: Summarize the results from different performance metrics

panels.description: The average throughput of all benchmarks (except noop) and all terminal values. See **Throughput Trends** for more details.

targets.rawSql:
SELECT 
	date AS "time",
	AVG(daily_benchmark_avg.avg_benchmark_change) * 100 AS "avg throughput change per benchmark type"
FROM (
	SELECT
	  date,
	  benchmark_type,
	  AVG(benchmark_change.change) AS "avg_benchmark_change"
	FROM (
	  SELECT
		  time,
		  DATE(time) as "date",
		  ((metrics->>'throughput')::numeric - 
		    FIRST_VALUE((metrics->>'throughput')::numeric) OVER(PARTITION BY benchmark_type,terminals order by time ASC)) /
		    FIRST_VALUE((metrics->>'throughput')::numeric) OVER(PARTITION BY benchmark_type,terminals order by time ASC) as "change",
		  terminals,
		  benchmark_type
	  FROM oltpbench_results
	  WHERE
		  $__timeFilter("time") AND
 		  query_mode = 'extended' AND
  		client_time = 60 AND
  		git_branch = 'origin/master' AND
  		wal_device = '$wal_device' AND
  		max_connection_threads = 32
	  ORDER BY time DESC
	) AS benchmark_change
	GROUP BY benchmark_type, date
	ORDER BY date DESC
) as daily_benchmark_avg
GROUP BY date
ORDER BY date

  max_connection_threads = 32
